      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-challenge&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;The Challenge &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#the-challenge&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Transitioning a massive fleet from legacy Ubuntu 16.04/ROS1 to a modern, secure ROS2 environment.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;the-impact&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;The Impact &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#the-impact&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build Times:&lt;/strong&gt; Reduced by &lt;strong&gt;66%&lt;/strong&gt; through Docker optimization.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security:&lt;/strong&gt; Implemented SROS2 for encrypted communication.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scale:&lt;/strong&gt; Successfully deployed to hundreds of robots in production.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
